9. 실행 순서
============================================================

1. m0609 + RG2 virtual bringup
ros2 launch m0609_rg2_bringup bringup.launch.py mode:=virtual model:=m0609

2. rosbridge 실행
ros2 launch rosbridge_server rosbridge_websocket_launch.xml

3. tf2_web_republisher 실행
ros2 run tf2_web_republisher tf2_web_republisher_node

4. 프론트 실행
cd ~/rokey/pjt_heu/DoosanRokey_B_1/burger_kiosk
npm run dev

